@danedmiston9673 as someone who has to deal with sand and mud very often, I wonder what kinds of pressures and flow rates can be achieved with this. 

We have a deep water well with a off the shelf submersible on the farm, but every now and then the muck gets in there and the motor burns itself out. 

But then again, you do run into size constraints with the ol' borehole.
